des:
You can simply ask Alexa to control your “Air purifier”. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our “BriSync” app in app market then register an account;
(2). Configure our devices in our “BriSync” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, iOS or Amazon app market then configures Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4). Search “BriSync” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5). Enable “BriSync” skill, and you'll be navigated to “BriSync” login page;
(6). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7). Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the Air Purifier.”
“Alexa, turn off the Air Purifier.”
“Alexa, set the Air Purifier fan Speed to Turbo.”
"Alexa, set the Air Purifier to Sleep Mode"
